"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## The last few weeks at Guild have been incredibly exciting!\\n\\nIf you‚Äôre new to Guild, allow us to get you up to speed. Guilds allow DAOs to token gate their communication channels via NFT, ERC-20, Mirror edition, POAP, whitelisted addresses, or any combination of the above. A guildhall also provides a single point of entry for your community members, replacing regular Discord links.\\n\\nOh, and did we mention we‚Äôre chain agnostic? Below are the chains we support so far:\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/guildxyz/status/1461723390549663758.](https://twitter.com/guildxyz/status/1461723390549663758.)\\n\\nTo date users of the Guild alpha have created a total of 309 Guildhalls, and our Medusa bot is live in 137 Discord servers. Telegram functionality is in the works and will come next.\\n\\n## Last week, Guildhalls went live\\n\\nGuildhalls enable DAOs to create multiple tiers of token-gated access, or allow DAOs to assign members roles relevant to their place in the DAO. Sismo was one of the first DAOs to set up a Guildhall.\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/guildxyz/status/1460665383225114630](https://twitter.com/guildxyz/status/1460665383225114630)\\n\\n‚ÄúZikies‚Äù (DAO members) gained roles in the guild depending on when they joined Sismo.\\n\\n## We also saw an epic collaboration between BLVCKHVND and Krause House\\n\\nAfter contributing 10 ETH to Krause House‚Äôs Mirror crowdfund, BLVCKHVND created a guild to form a cross-DAO communication channel.\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/blvkhvnd/status/1461802276654403589](https://twitter.com/blvkhvnd/status/1461802276654403589)\\n\\nThey also opened the guild up to friendly communities with significant overlap, including Friends with Benefits, the Parallel Alpha community, and Forefront.\\n\\nTo join BLVCKHVND‚Äôs guild, one must hold either 100 $HVND, 75 $FWB, $100 $KRAUSE, a Parallel Alpha NFT, or 1000 $FF in their wallet. You can join the guild here: <https://alpha.guild.xyz/blvkhvnd>\\n\\n## Finally, ecodao has formed a guild\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/ecodao_/status/1461810075203522571](https://twitter.com/ecodao_/status/1461810075203522571)\\n\\n‚Ä¶but what if a guild was formed for all of the impact DAOs to collaborate? ü§î\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/guildxyz/status/1462792143429378050](https://twitter.com/guildxyz/status/1462792143429378050)\\n\\n**We‚Äôre still in alpha but we love to see DAOs begin to utilize our tooling and experiment with cross-DAO channels. If you form a guild for your DAO, tag us on Twitter so we can mention you in the next round-up.**\\n\\n**Twitter: <https://twitter.com/guildxyz>**\",\"timestamp\":1638219313,\"title\":\"Guild Update - Nov. 29, 2021\"},\"digest\":\"YVS2tmYKmqxgpXNrSZXN0bJasb76V0d_IqXDO6JXEuI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x5ccb0a3274ABf16d03C57fdfcB82f06389a33FAB\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FR7r4t-ILhThCyv_Y-guE50rIv0_FxVyVUVqIjG1LnY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qlYa_hUhgNOqNOn65-QCovNemaq95FAIBHC60UnYTnY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"_rUrWE32M8-BsENTIihCfnDK33WsKQZw-kbu7accxHT1DCYywbn08EJ8N1jatHylqbzX5QG8n6W5PcAzsCO2Yw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x0ad63c907c2443128d8a996d1049d8a4eaf629dafa7dae3bf4bf4a0ded1234911afa3e8591fe220e8ae565e194ddce63f8b3bb20494b60e39441b7aa65d2a6991b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FR7r4t-ILhThCyv_Y-guE50rIv0_FxVyVUVqIjG1LnY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qlYa_hUhgNOqNOn65-QCovNemaq95FAIBHC60UnYTnY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"-vrGyrrAT6HEv5ehystaACgmeHA2GNaNKGTSICX_ejc\"}"